name: HURTED - RIANTI
description:
sometimes people feel that he is the one who is hurt the most, maybe he forgets to turn his head and observe who is hurt more than him, who unknowingly hurts others, this picture visualizes people who can deliberately close their eyes so they are not blessed with look and care about one another, or he is forced to close his eyes because he wants to be more appreciated, and the character in this picture I named "RIANTI"

DIGITAL DRAWING 5000 x 5000 Pixel
